      "writtenOn": "2020-07-11T02:18:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "to me, whether it uses OnBuild or OnTagIndex is an implementation detail of search. The exposing them both means that caller has to choose between the two. I think it would be simpler for the caller if there was one function Fetch() which chooses between the two. Note that this is how python version is implemented.",
      "parentUuid": "b1db469a_3f5c410d",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 110,
        "startChar": 21,
